			<p>I took a classroom RPG from theory through game design to a revenue product, following my own governance pipeline end to end. It proved the system works -- and honestly showed where it doesn't. I'm including the full post-mortem because honest failures teach more than polished wins.</p>
		</span>
		<span slot="elevated">
			<p>
				Aetheria is the project that proves the system works — and honestly reveals where it doesn't. It traveled the complete I→II→III path: from gamification theory to game design to revenue product. I directed the comprehensive post-mortem below because honest reflection on what failed teaches more than polished success stories.<Cite id={1} author="Ries, Eric" title="The Lean Startup" source="Crown Business" year={2011} />
			</p>
